    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Members of the Woman's club\nwill hold open house in their new\nclub building on Ninth and Walnut\nthis afternoon. Members of all the\nwoman's clubs In the city have\nbeen invited to inspect the appoint\nments of the new quarters, and re-\nceiving hours will be from 2 until\ns o'clock.\n\n\nTomorrow evening the club will\nofficially open the cottage at 8\nO'Clock, and at that time entertain\nment fof the members and their\nhusbands and a few friends will\nbe provided."
    }
  ]
